.SH Description
.PP
Collins power lets you change or list the current status of an asset if
it has been configured properly with IPMI.
.SS Power Examples
.PP
Show the current status.
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
collins power --status -t M001
\f[R]
.fi
.PP
Power down an asset.
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
collins power -t M00001 -p off
\f[R]
.fi
